53
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:28,210
You said you're fine with anyone else.

54
00:03:28,210 --> 00:03:30,320
Is San Ha just anyone?

55
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:34,580
Exactly. He's more trustworthy and reliable.

56
00:03:34,580 --> 00:03:36,300
You like Kim San Ha more than me at times.

57
00:03:36,300 --> 00:03:37,780
I'm telling you no.

58
00:03:37,780 --> 00:03:40,570
Don't just say no outright.

59
00:03:40,570 --> 00:03:44,320
- Give it some thought– 
 - There's nothing to think about.

60
