74
00:04:45,870 --> 00:04:48,770
That was truly nonsense, though.

75
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:52,150
It won't be good if you keep treating me like this.

76
00:04:52,150 --> 00:04:55,570
Don't you know how important my role is right now?

77
00:04:55,570 --> 00:04:57,870
I trust you, Oppa.

78
00:04:57,870 --> 00:05:00,230
Hey, you, too.

79
00:05:00,230 --> 00:05:02,760
"I trust you, Hyungnim."

80
00:05:03,590 --> 00:05:06,080
It's natural for him to oppose us.

81
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:10,660
How could anyone give a daughter like Joo Won so easily?

82
00:05:10,660 --> 00:05:13,430
Any dad would feel she's too precious.

83
00:05:13,430 --> 00:05:15,590
I would feel that way, too.

84
00:05:23,350 --> 00:05:25,110
Don't worry.

85
00:05:25,110 --> 00:05:27,440
I'm right here.

86
00:05:28,890 --> 00:05:30,420
Me, too.

87
00:05:46,260 --> 00:05:49,020
You always tell them it's the heart that counts.

88
00:05:49,020 --> 00:05:52,640
Why are you acting all dramatic out here?

89
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:55,130
My goodness.

90
00:06:01,300 --> 00:06:03,410
Is it because it's too sudden?

91
00:06:03,410 --> 00:06:06,840
Even so, how could you leave so sternly?

92
00:06:12,810 --> 00:06:17,610
Wait, is it because you don't like San Ha as Joo Won's match?

93
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:23,520
Yes, I don't.

94
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:29,850
A single dad with an only daughter. I wanted to show off my daughter.

95
00:06:29,850 --> 00:06:33,120
But I can't, so I'm sorry.

96
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:38,320
And I don't like that with him I'd never be able to side with my poor daughter as I wish.

97
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:42,420
Did I tell you not to show off your daughter? Go ahead.

98
00:06:42,420 --> 00:06:45,050
Is San Ha someone who'd make Joo Won suffer?

99
