104
00:07:04,100 --> 00:07:07,800
Come on. They're different from San Ha's mom and me.

105
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:10,850
And it's not like they're getting married right now.

106
00:07:10,850 --> 00:07:12,960
That's what I'm worried about.

107
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:15,960
What happens if they decide they won't work out anymore?

108
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:22,150
Will you tell them to go back to being a good brother and sister?

109
00:07:23,620 --> 00:07:27,460
You know they're not the type to bring this up lightly.

110
00:07:27,460 --> 00:07:31,160
That's why I'm against them. That's exactly why.

111
00:07:32,660 --> 00:07:35,200
Will you really make them swear,

112
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:39,080
"You two better not break up, no matter what happens"

113
00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:41,540
when this is their first relationship?

114
00:07:45,470 --> 00:07:49,440
When my daughter is sad or suffering,

115
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:53,490
"Come home anytime. I'm on your side, no matter what."

116
00:07:53,490 --> 00:07:55,570
I want to say that.

117
00:07:55,570 --> 00:07:58,930
But it's San Ha. How can I say that?

118
00:08:02,750 --> 00:08:04,950
I'll only think about my Joo Won.

119
00:08:04,950 --> 00:08:07,680
So don't bring this up again.

120
00:08:08,330 --> 00:08:09,890
Mr. Yoon.

121
00:08:11,660 --> 00:08:16,470
Okay, fine. I'll only think about San Ha, too.

122
00:08:16,470 --> 00:08:19,350
Yes, I'll only worry about him.

