144
00:10:04,730 --> 00:10:09,730
 But how was my ponytail always so neat and tidy? 

145
00:10:09,730 --> 00:10:13,290
How were my clothes always so clean?

146
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:19,640
They asked how you raised me like that on your own.

147
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:22,270
I didn't want it to show that you didn't have a mom.

148
00:10:22,270 --> 00:10:24,850
 Exactly. 

149
00:10:24,850 --> 00:10:29,030
I grew up well without it showing that I didn't have a mom.

150
00:10:30,020 --> 00:10:35,460
You raised me properly with a lot of love.

151
00:10:35,460 --> 00:10:37,650
You can trust me.

